query:
UPDATE people.examiners
            SET
                first_name = COALESCE($3, first_name),
                last_name = COALESCE($4, last_name),
                shortcode = COALESCE($5, shortcode),
                female = COALESCE($6, female),
                am = COALESCE($7, am),
                pm = COALESCE($8, pm),
                checked_in = COALESCE($9, checked_in)
            WHERE id = $1 AND session_id = $2
